%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor PM as Project Manager

participant UI as Dependency Detail UI
participant BFF as Dependency Management BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant DEP as Dependency Service
participant ADP as Service Adapter
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}

PM->>UI: Assign or change assignee
UI->>BFF: Submit assignee update
BFF->>ORCH: Start owner assignment flow
ORCH->>DEP: Validate dependency is not closed
DEP->>READDB: Read project_dependency
READDB-->>DEP: Current dependency state
DEP-->>ORCH: Validation success
ORCH->>DEP: Save assignee update
DEP->>PRIMARYDB: Update project_dependency (assignee_user_id, assigned_date)
PRIMARYDB-->>DEP: Save success
DEP-->>ORCH: Assignment success
ORCH->>ADP: Notify new assignee
ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish DependencyAssigned Event
ORCH-->>BFF: Success
BFF-->>UI: Show updated assignee
